steps

1) install angular
2) create project 
3) add 3 routes namely 
	mainPage	=====> get a list of state + ut
	statePage	=====>	open via clicking on particular state. display state data and list of district
	districtPage	=====>  open respective district and show data

4) add api and populate data on desired page;

5) add dependencies
	ng2-google-chart or chart.js for demographic data
	lazy loading

6) add css
7) make page responsive
 
